snippet.title: SAVE Playtest Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
SAVE is a survival deep sea horror game for 1-4 co-op game, sets in the eerie depths of an abandoned 6,000-Ton Ship 'SENARA', where every shadow holds a secret, and every corner could be your last. Unravel the mysteries and safely escape avoiding relentless threats that prowl in the darkness.
